title: Ep. 17 Younger Men, Divorce, and Family Matters
description:
This week Kiki, Medinah, and Shayla Raye are back! Kiki and Medinah discuss meeting the family, and Shayla shares her love for younger men. The ladies also dive into divorce, breakups and bouncing back.

Remember to send all questions to cocktales.atl@gmail.com
